\par Components: V, S
\par Casting Time: 1 action
\par Range: Close (25 ft. + 5 ft./2 levels)
\par Target: 1 lb. of wood/level, all within a 20-ft. radius
\par Duration: Instantaneous
\par Saving Throw: Will negates (object)
\par Spell Resistance: Yes (0bject)
