\par Components: V, S, M/DF
\par Casting Time: 1 action
\par Range: Touch
\par Target: Living creatures touched
\par Duration: 2 hours/level (see text)
\par Saving Throw: Will negates (harmless)
\par Spell Resistance: Yes (harmless)
